The Light House Cinema bụ ihe nkiri nka nwere oche 614 gafee ihuenyo anọ na Dublin, Ireland, nke na-ejekwa ozi dị ka otu n'ime ebe maka Dublin International Film Festival.
Site na afọ 1988 na afọ 1996, ụlọ ihe nkiri Light House mbụ dị n'ebe a na-eme ihe nkiri na Middle Abbey Street
E wuru ụlọ ihe nkiri ọhụrụ gọmentị kwadoro ma meghee ya na Smithfield, Dublin na afọ 2008
Ọ mechiri n'oge na-adịghị anya na afọ 2011 mgbe ihe onwunwe Dublin dara, mana e weghaara ihe onwunwa ahụ na National Asset Management Agency (NAMA).
N'afọ 2012, Element Pictures weghaara ihe nkiri ahụ ma meghee ya ọzọ
Kemgbe ahụ, ọ ghọrọ ihe ịga nke ọma ma bụrụ nke a ma ama n'etiti ndị obodo ahụ, n'ihi ngwakọta ihe nkiri ya na-agụnye ụlọ nka na Hollywood blockbusters, yana ihe ngosi oge niile.
Ihe nkiri ahụ na-enwekwa abalị ajụjụ, klọb akwụkwọ, ihe ngosi ihe nkiri ofufe pụrụ iche, na mmemme egwu ihe nkiri a na-akpọ 'One Two One Two Music Festival'.
Ihe nkiri 1 nwere ndị na-ege ntị 277; Ihe nkiri 2 nwere 153; Ihe nkiri 3 nwere 116; Ihe nkiri 4 nwere 68.
